sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Card, Container } from "react-bootstrap" const Workout = ({workout}) => { return ( {workout.description} On {`${workout.date.substring(8,10)}.${workout.date.substring(5,7)}, ${workout.date.substring(11,16)} `} {`Price: ${workout.revenuePerClient} shekels`} Duration: { workout.duration > 1 ? `${workout.duration} hours` : `${workout.duration} hour` } ) } export default Workout
